attributes.title: Bubble bursting at 18,000fps
attributes.description: In the slowest video they have ever done, Gav and Dan slow down the moment a bubble pops by over 700 times. This is the first time we've used the Phantom v1610 which shoots at 18,000fps at 720p. This camera is absolutely mental!

attributes.title: Exploding lighters at 1000fps
attributes.description: In the first video from the archive, Dan forgot to bring the meat to the bqq, so he cooked the lighters.

attributes.title: Smashing a TV with a Hammer
attributes.description: In the next video from the archive, Gav and Dan show you what happens when a TV from the late 80s meets a hammer from the late 90s.
attributes.display_title: Smashing a TV with a Hammer

attributes.title: Tuning Fork at 1600fps
attributes.description: A bunch of people requested a tuning fork so... BOOM! Here's a video of a tuning fork.

attributes.title: Cat Jumping in Slow Motion
attributes.description: To Gav and Dan's dismay, viewer feedback indicates that Lloyd the cat is in fact the most popular member of the Slow Mo Guys team. So here is a short and sweet clip of Lloyd in action. Oh and by the way, Lloyd is a female cat... that's right.

attributes.title: Jackie Chan Coin Challenge
attributes.description: Gav and Dan put their hand-eye coordination skills to the test. Due to the fact that both of them were terrible, we had to resort to a montage. Oh and for the record, Jackie Chan definitely did more than 3.

attributes.title: Paint Exploding at 15,000fps
attributes.description: Gav and Dan find an interesting way to paint ceilings 600 times slower than you can see with your regular human eyeball!

attributes.title: Banger Week - Exploding Fertility Statue
attributes.description: It's Monday! It's day 1 of banger week. Come back every day this week for a new explosion. Today, Gav and Dan blow up a weird Peruvian fertility statue.

attributes.title: Banger Week Day 2 - Bowl of Cereal
attributes.description: Start your Tuesday with an ACTION BREAKFAST! Banger Week continues!
attributes.display_title: Banger Week Day 2 - Bowl of Cereal

attributes.title: Banger Week Day 3 - Lego House
attributes.description: It's Wednesday of Banger Week! Wednesday sounds like a good day for Gav and Dan to destroy childhood memories.

attributes.title: Banger Week Day 4 - Planet Earth
attributes.description: Day 4 of Banger Week! Today, as promised, Gav and Dan blow up the world!

attributes.title: Banger Week Day 5 - Giant Paint Explosion
attributes.description: It's the final day of Banger Week! Gav and Dan blow up paint tins in what easily is the messiest and bloodiest episode ever.
attributes.display_title: Banger Week Day 5 - Giant Paint Explosion

attributes.title: Surface Tension Droplets at 2500fps
attributes.description: Gav and Dan whip out their best globules just for you! This video shows you the amazing bouncing water droplet effect super close up and super slow.

attributes.title: Crossbow vs Dr Pepper TEN at 2500fps
attributes.description: Gav ruins some perfectly good beverages with a crossbow IN SUPER SLOW MOTION!
attributes.display_title: Crossbow vs Dr Pepper TEN at 2500fps

attributes.title: Underwater Bullets at 27,000fps
attributes.description: Gav and Dan slow down time by over one thousand times to show you how bullets look when fired from an underwater gun.

attributes.title: Water Balloon Fight with 1500 people Starring Freddie Wong
attributes.description: Gav and Dan start a water balloon fight with over a thousand people and film it at 2500fps. It does not end well for them.

attributes.title: Behind the Scenes of the RTX Water Balloon Fight
attributes.description: At RTX 2013, the Slow Mo Guys took on Freddie W and 1,000 Rooster Teeth fans in a slow motion water balloon fight!
attributes.display_title: Behind the Scenes of the RTX Water Balloon Fight

attributes.title: Slow Mo Car Explosion - The Slow Mo Guys
attributes.description: This week Gav blows up a car in slow motion. My favourite part is the bit with the explosion. Shot with a Phantom Flex at 2500fps Slow Mo Car Explosion - The Slow Mo Guys
attributes.display_title: Slow Mo Car Explosion - The Slow Mo Guys

attributes.title: Beer Bottle Trick at 2500fps - The Slow Mo Guys
attributes.description: Gav and Dan find an interesting way to destroy their bev bottles while showing off some cool science.
attributes.display_title: Beer Bottle Trick at 2500fps - The Slow Mo Guys

attributes.title: Super Hydrophobic Surface and Magnetic Liquid
attributes.description: Gav and Dan are in the GE lab using nanotechnology to show you cool liquid physics at 2500fps.
attributes.display_title: Super Hydrophobic Surface and Magnetic Liquid

attributes.title: Melon Fragmentation at 2500fps
attributes.description: If the military made melon grenades, they would probably look like this.

attributes.title: Fully Automatic Assault Rifle at 18,000fps
attributes.description: BEWARE, LOUD VIDEO! Watch in HD. (No 1080p available with this camera).Gav and Dan head to Alabama to show you the mechanical workings of a fully automatic M4 Carbine with holographic sight as it fires 30 rounds in just over 2 seconds. Dan is in the British Army and has vast gun experience. Gav only has experience with an Xbox controller.

attributes.title: Airbag
attributes.description: Gav and Dan show how fast car airbags inflate by filming them at 2500fps. Research has shown that the only thing that has ever inflated faster, is Dan's ego.

attributes.title: Mousetrap Chain Reaction
attributes.description: Gav sets up a chain of 150 mousetraps. Dan sets them off bravely.

attributes.title: Cannon Firing in Slow Motion
attributes.description: Gav and Dan are given a cannon by Captain Morgan White and swiftly make use of it by blasting a pyramid of drinks.

attributes.title: Swim Cap Trick in Slow Motion
attributes.description: Summer is well on the way! With it, Gav and Dan show you how to save time when you bung on your swimming cap. Then, they show you what it looked like in lovely slow motion. Kind of defeats the purpose of doing it fast in the first place, to be honest.
attributes.display_title: Swim Cap Trick in Slow Motion

attributes.title: Giant Bubbles Popping in Slow Motion
attributes.description: In this video, Gav and Dan introduce you to the mesmerizing and colorful world of bubbles popping 100 times slower than you can see with your eye.
attributes.display_title: Giant Bubbles Popping in Slow Motion

attributes.title: Slow Motion Vomit
attributes.description: Warning, this episode is absolutely minging. The title pretty much says it all.

attributes.title: Leaping Slow Motion Doggy

attributes.display_title: Convertible Aerodynamics at 1000fps - The Slow Mo Guys
